  "instructions": [
    "Heat the donabe over medium heat and add olive oil until shimmering.",
    "Add the sliced onion and sauté until translucent and fragrant.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic, grated ginger, and harissa paste, cooking for 1 minute.",
    "Add the beef cubes, browning all sides on each side.",
    "Sprinkle in the cumin, coriander, and cinnamon, stirring to coat the meat.",
    "Pour in the beef stock and bring to a gentle simmer, covering the pot.",
    "Reduce heat to low, add halved apricots, and cook for 90 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Finish with a splash of lemon juice, season with salt and pepper, and garnish with chopped cilantro before serving."
